<BaseLayout
  title="Seniors & Family Pharmacy Care | Four Winds Roots Pharmacy, North York"
  description="Pharmacy services for seniors and caregivers in North York — blister packaging, free delivery, MedsCheck, and personal service at Four Winds Roots Pharmacy. Call (416) 398-8200."
>
  <!--
    IA KEY BLOCKS (from information-architecture.md — Seniors & Family Care):
