    2. Blister packaging highlight — ServiceCard linking to /services/blister-packaging
    3. Free delivery highlight — ServiceCard linking to /services/free-delivery
    4. MedsCheck highlight — ServiceCard linking to /services/medication-reviews
    5. Reviews — 1-2 ReviewCards from senior/caregiver patients (real, compliant, with consent)
