  <div class="container section">
    <h1>Pharmacy Care for Seniors &amp; Families in North York</h1>
    <p>
      Managing medications shouldn't be a source of stress. At Four Winds Roots Pharmacy,
      we take the time to make it easier — with free blister packaging, free delivery, and
      a pharmacist who will actually sit down with you.
    </p>

    <section aria-labelledby="seniors-blister">
      <h2 id="seniors-blister">Blister Packaging — Never Miss a Dose</h2>
      <p>
        We organise your prescriptions into individual sealed blister packs, labelled by day
        and time, so there's no guesswork about what to take when.
        <strong>Blister packaging is included at no extra cost</strong> with your prescriptions
        at Four Winds Roots — confirmed by the Ontario Health atHome directory.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/services/blister-packaging" class="btn btn-secondary">About Blister Packaging &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="seniors-delivery">
      <h2 id="seniors-delivery">Free Delivery to Your Door</h2>
      <p>
        We deliver prescriptions for free across North York — including blister packs.
        No delivery charge, no minimum order. If getting out is difficult,
        we bring your medications to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/services/free-delivery" class="btn btn-secondary">About Free Delivery &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="seniors-medscheck">
      <h2 id="seniors-medscheck">Free MedsCheck Medication Reviews</h2>
      <p>
        MedsCheck is a free, government-funded review under the Ontario Drug Benefit program.
        If you take three or more prescription medications for a chronic condition, you likely
        qualify. Your pharmacist sits with you privately, goes through everything you're taking,
        and gives you a written summary to keep.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/services/medication-reviews" class="btn btn-secondary">Book a MedsCheck &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="seniors-caregivers">
      <h2 id="seniors-caregivers">Helping Caregivers Too</h2>
      <p>
        Coordinating a family member's medications from a distance is hard work.
        Call us on their behalf — we can help manage refills, arrange delivery,
        set up blister packaging, and answer your questions. We're here to make
        it easier for the whole family.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="seniors-call">
      <h2 id="seniors-call">Call Us — We're Here to Help</h2>
      <p>Our pharmacists take the time to talk. No rush, no jargon.</p>
      <PhoneLink class="btn btn-call" display="Call (416) 398-8200" />
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
